data.description: Welcome to your cozy new home! Situated in the delightful heart of Le Mars, this home offers easy access to downtown shops, restaurants, schools, and parks. Upon arrival, you'll be greeted by a cozy carport that easily accommodates two vehicles, ensuring your convenience. Step through the front door to discover an inviting, open living space with wooden beamed ceilings and a wonderfully unique kitchen. The entire home has been recently refreshed with a coat of paint, giving it a pristine, welcoming feel. Walking down the hallway you'll find a bathroom, a comfy bedroom, and your primary suite. The primary bedroom offers ample space and includes its own private bathroom, providing you with a comfortable retreat. As you enter the basement you'll find a carpeted bedroom complemented by charming wooden sliding doors and walls. Additionally, there is another room with a closet that could be used for anything. The utility room has a sink, washer/dryer hook ups, your furnace, water heater, and electrical panel. As you step outside into the backyard, you'll be delighted by the greenery. The lot has apple, peach, pear, and plum trees, enhancing your outdoor experience. Alley access provides added convenience, making this backyard a versatile space for all your outdoor activities. Did I mention you get to live in the "Ice Cream Capital of the World"? Agent has close family relation with Sellers.
